= IMG_LoadTexture =

Load an image directly into a render texture.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
SDL_Texture * IMG_LoadTexture(SDL_Renderer *renderer, const char *file);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''renderer'''
|SDL Render
|-
|'''file'''
|image file name
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns SDL Texture, or NULL on error

